[Any score draw gives 2 points to both clubs!]

Final [May 21]
Porto          0-2 Sport
Sport winners of second phase of second stage.
 
Sport won second stage by winning both phases.

Sport won 1997 Pernambuco Championship by winning both stages.

Relegated: Ypiranga and Centro Limoeirense.

Topscorer: Leonardo (Sport) 14 goals.


